asciinema: asciinema (a tool for recording terminal sessions)
asciinema:
asciinema: asciinema (aka asciinema CLI or asciinema recorder) is a 
asciinema: command-line tool for recording and live streaming terminal
asciinema: sessions.
asciinema:
asciinema: Unlike typical screen recording software, which records 
asciinema: visual output of a screen into a heavyweight video files,
asciinema: asciinema CLI runs inside a terminal, capturing terminal
asciinema: session output into a lightweight recording files in the
asciinema: asciicast format, or streaming it live in real-time.
